= Decision Matrix

#info-box[
  *Assessment Result:*

  #checkbox *PASS* - Move to Full Mock Simulations (if 2+ passing assessments achieved)

  #checkbox *CONDITIONAL PASS* - Take another section assessment

  #checkbox *REVIEW NEEDED* - Review weak areas, then reassess

  #checkbox *REPEAT TOPICS* - Return to CR or RC lessons before reassessing
]

